Any production or use of a client which impersonates the identification, authentication, or any data submitted by an approved Affix Software Program is forbidden. Impersonation of other users (without the User’s specific permission and without identifying oneself as themself) is forbidden . Users are NOT allowed to modify any Team Affix file in any way, and any modification is forbidden. Users however may submit requests via the Team Affix website https://teamaffix.wixsite.com/affix . 
If there are any issues with our programs, feel free to report them, and if there are any requests you would like to make, feel free to write to us. You may use our website, or email us at "teamaffix.contact@gmail.com".
